21:49.709 --> 21:51.478
What did you do then?

21:51.544 --> 21:53.279
I showed him the pictures
of them together.

21:53.346 --> 21:55.682
And how did he
respond to that?

21:55.748 --> 21:57.850
He--

21:57.917 --> 21:59.819
He got so angry.

22:01.020 --> 22:02.422
He told me to leave.

22:02.489 --> 22:05.257
He said he'd never
give me my money back.

22:05.324 --> 22:07.026
And then he threatened me.

22:07.093 --> 22:08.495
He threatened you?

22:08.561 --> 22:10.397
Said he'd call the police,
have me arrested.

22:10.463 --> 22:11.731
Then he--

22:13.500 --> 22:16.369
