toward the door.

22:31.751 --> 22:33.052
And he--

22:34.821 --> 22:36.723
he picked up
a pair of scissors,

22:36.789 --> 22:39.225
and...

22:39.291 --> 22:40.927
came at me again.

22:40.993 --> 22:42.028
What did you do?

22:42.094 --> 22:44.797
I grabbed the nearest
thing I could

22:44.864 --> 22:45.898
to defend myself.

22:45.965 --> 22:47.066
The trophy.

22:48.868 --> 22:50.369
He lunged at me.

22:50.437 --> 22:52.371
I thought he was
going to kill me,

22:52.439 --> 22:54.941
