I had no choice.

23:00.312 --> 23:02.081
I'm so, so sorry.

23:06.118 --> 23:07.987
- ...as soon as possible.
- Right.

23:09.288 --> 23:10.356
Detectives.

23:10.423 --> 23:11.991
