23:12.058 --> 23:14.360
Kind of ballsy of her to put
her client on the stand.

23:14.427 --> 23:15.628
Could've backfired.

23:15.695 --> 23:18.030
Mrs. Allen was
a compelling witness.

23:18.097 --> 23:19.432
What's your gut?

23:19.499 --> 23:21.100
We'll see.

23:21.167 --> 23:23.536
