give you a heads up.

23:38.184 --> 23:39.686
Should've taken that bet.

23:39.752 --> 23:41.420
Asshole.

23:41.488 --> 23:43.122
Headed
back to the house?

23:43.189 --> 23:45.658
I gotta go do this thing
with Benitez.

23:45.725 --> 23:47.960
The Holland case?
How's that going?

23:48.027 --> 23:50.930
In a rational world,
it'd be a slam dunk.

23:52.499 --> 23:55.134
She's kind of a dish,
Benitez.

23:55.201 --> 23:56.636
Is she?

23:56.703 --> 23:58.304
