who's age appropriate.

23:58.370 --> 23:59.539
Fuck you.

23:59.606 --> 24:01.440
You ought to ask her out.

24:01.508 --> 24:02.509
We're working together.

24:02.575 --> 24:03.843
That's never stopped you.

24:11.751 --> 24:13.452
