want to join us?

24:13.520 --> 24:14.887
I know he's
under house arrest,

24:14.954 --> 24:16.523
but I'm sure he's allowed
in the driveway.

24:16.589 --> 24:18.658
He's fine where he is.
Thank you.

24:18.725 --> 24:20.426
On the night Donatella Spear
was murdered--

24:20.493 --> 24:22.361
That has not been
proved, counselor.

24:22.428 --> 24:23.395
Please.

24:23.462 --> 24:24.731
On October 12 of last year,

24:24.797 --> 24:26.432
Miss Spear
arrived at 8:32 p.m.

24:26.499 --> 24:28.535
We have security data
and video.

24:28.601 --> 24:31.203
Someone exited the house,
no video, at 11:20 p.m.

24:31.270 --> 24:32.805
Mr. Holland and Miss Spear.

24:32.872 --> 24:35.307
And through the main vehicle
entrance 14 minutes later.

24:35.374 --> 24:36.643
He was driving her home

24:36.709 --> 24:38.578
after an evening
of consensual relations.

24:38.645 --> 24:40.680
He's a real gentleman.
She was already dead.

24:40.747 --> 24:42.882
No. Alive and well.

24:42.949 --> 24:46.986
14 minutes from the house
to the car and out the gate?

24:47.053 --> 24:48.721
Well, they'd had
a lot to drink.

24:48.788 --> 24:50.222
They'd done some Ecstasy.

24:50.289 --> 24:54.193
And they were still in a--
let's call it a frisky mood.

24:54.260 --> 24:55.595
Making out. Parking.

24:55.662 --> 24:57.229
Ever do it, Bosch,
in your youth?

24:57.296 --> 24:59.799
Maybe he was trying to put
a seat belt on a corpse.

24:59.866 --> 25:02.168
Someone-- Mr. Holland,
presumably--

25:02.234 --> 25:05.371
returned through that gate
at 1:52 a.m.

25:05.437 --> 25:07.206
Holland told us
he dropped off Spear

25:07.273 --> 25:09.508
at her house
around midnight,

25:09.576 --> 25:11.477
was back here by 12:30.

25:11.544 --> 25:13.880
That's nearly 90 minutes
unaccounted for.

25:13.946 --> 25:15.181
He was mistaken
about the time.

25:15.247 --> 25:16.248
He was under the influence.

25:16.315 --> 25:17.483
Bosch, who knows

25:17.550 --> 25:19.318
where the fuck
the time goes, right?

25:19.385 --> 25:20.887
They were fucked up.
Why would he lie

25:20.953 --> 25:22.822
about something
that's so easy to check?

25:22.889 --> 25:24.256
Because he's
an arrogant prick.

25:24.323 --> 25:25.324
You would know.

25:25.391 --> 25:27.459
Let me ask you
something, Rudy.

25:27.526 --> 25:28.995
You miss the job?

25:29.061 --> 25:31.030
Fuck, no.
Not for a second.

25:31.097 --> 25:32.565
I was never a lifer
like you.

25:32.632 --> 25:34.533
Oh, yeah, right.

25:34.601 --> 25:37.503
20 years of just
going through the motions.

25:37.570 --> 25:40.206
But pimping for celebrities?
That's low.

25:40.272 --> 25:42.709
That's low even for
a bottom feeder like you.

25:42.775 --> 25:45.111
Bosch, Bosch, Bosch.

25:45.177 --> 25:46.445
Look at you.

25:46.512 --> 25:48.848
Most guys would've
pulled the pin,

25:48.915 --> 25:53.485
take the pension,
lean back, enjoy life.

25:53.552 --> 25:55.121
Except you got none.

25:56.889 --> 25:59.726
When the department finally
puts you out to pasture,

25:59.792 --> 26:01.661
you'll eat your gun.

26:16.342 --> 26:18.611
40 minutes
door to door in traffic.

26:18.678 --> 26:20.880
That night,
that hour? Under ten.

26:24.717 --> 26:26.285
I've been here at night.

26:26.352 --> 26:27.687
It's dark dark.

26:28.587 --> 26:30.022
Private.

26:30.089 --> 26:31.090
He uses her keys,

26:31.157 --> 26:33.159
drags her body
up the stairs,

26:33.225 --> 26:34.093
stages a scene.

26:34.160 --> 26:35.695
There's your missing
90 minutes.

26:35.762 --> 26:37.163
He must have had help.

26:37.229 --> 26:38.765
Rudy Tafero's my bet.

26:38.831 --> 26:40.599
We've been at this
for 13 months.

26:40.667 --> 26:42.234
