26:43.502 --> 26:46.005
Ran the phone records.
No calls.

26:46.072 --> 26:48.174
The place was wiped clean.
That's suspicious.

26:48.240 --> 26:49.241
It's all suspicious.

26:49.308 --> 26:51.343
And if Holland
were an ordinary mook

26:51.410 --> 26:52.578
with a public defender,

26:52.645 --> 26:54.213
he'd be begging
to cop a plea.

26:54.280 --> 26:56.315
