film director

26:56.382 --> 26:57.817
with a high-priced
mouthpiece.

26:57.884 --> 26:59.085
Well, I still think
he'll plead.

26:59.151 --> 27:01.788
This is L.A. I got
two words for you.

27:01.854 --> 27:02.989
