27:15.668 --> 27:17.236
He leaves. She wants
to get off again.

27:17.303 --> 27:19.906
Auto-erotic asphyxiation
is a male phenomenon.

27:19.972 --> 27:22.408
- There are cases of females--
- Very few.

27:22.474 --> 27:23.843
A few is all they need.

27:23.910 --> 27:26.578
That's why your testimony
