27:48.234 --> 27:51.704
Head's like a baked apple.
No I.D.

27:51.771 --> 27:53.639
You glove up before
you went in, Powers?

27:53.706 --> 27:55.474
Yeah, I did.

27:55.541 --> 27:57.043
He's been cooking.

27:57.109 --> 27:59.311
Might want a hazmat
to go with those gloves.

28:11.490 --> 28:13.259
What was that about?

28:13.325 --> 28:14.626
Fucking Bosch.

28:32.144 --> 28:33.312
Jerry.

28:34.947 --> 28:36.783
"De Oppresso Liber."

28:37.683 --> 28:39.718
"Free the oppressed"?

28:40.753 --> 28:42.354
More like
