over at FSD.

28:56.769 --> 28:58.004
Air it the fuck out.

29:14.153 --> 29:14.921
Powers,

29:14.987 --> 29:16.455
you run the plates?

29:16.522 --> 29:17.990
I'm not a boot, Bosch.

29:18.057 --> 29:20.893
R-O comes back
to a male in Eagle Rock.

29:21.861 --> 29:23.162
Who called it in?

29:23.229 --> 29:24.797
Shopping cart lady
flagged us down.

29:24.864 --> 29:26.465
Door was open,
flapping in the breeze.

29:26.532 --> 29:28.000
Lock's busted.
Scene's fucked.

29:28.067 --> 29:29.335
People in and out,
stealing shit,

29:29.401 --> 29:31.904
- God knows what.
- This suit is toast.

29:31.971 --> 29:33.505
That looks kind of fresh.

29:35.607 --> 29:37.276
