at RHD.

29:50.056 --> 29:52.158
Doesn't mean
it always rings true
here on the streets.

29:52.224 --> 29:53.692
It should.

29:53.759 --> 29:54.726
Whatever.

29:54.793 --> 29:56.128
Come on, Harry.

29:59.065 --> 30:01.733
That tattoo.
