30:06.005 --> 30:07.306
You got one, too?

30:07.373 --> 30:09.541
- Want to see it?
- I'll pass.

30:19.818 --> 30:21.553
Lieutenant.

30:21.620 --> 30:23.355
Captain.

30:23.422 --> 30:24.991
This thing is bullshit.

30:25.057 --> 30:26.425
