some points off our people.

30:33.565 --> 30:36.335
Oh, it's just boilerplate
blame the police.

30:36.402 --> 30:39.571
Your lead detective
has a history.

30:39.638 --> 30:42.841
Uh, he has a history
of being accused.

30:42.909 --> 30:44.576
Where there's smoke.

30:44.643 --> 30:46.112
