the written.

30:53.785 --> 30:56.588
Oh, thanks.
Nervous about the orals.

30:56.655 --> 30:57.856
I don't see why.

30:57.924 --> 30:59.558
The orals should be
right up your alley.

31:00.626 --> 31:01.894
Excuse me?

31:13.639 --> 31:15.241
