31:31.623 --> 31:33.159
Morning, Juan.

31:38.597 --> 31:39.932
Homicide. He's out.

31:39.999 --> 31:42.234
I used to say it
as a joke, you know?

31:42.301 --> 31:43.235
Gentlemen.

31:43.302 --> 31:45.037
Lieutenant.

31:45.104 --> 31:46.805
