32:07.926 --> 32:09.628
- Yeah, you are.
- No I'm not.

32:09.695 --> 32:10.829
You guys headed downtown?

32:10.896 --> 32:12.098
Yeah, just leaving.

32:12.164 --> 32:14.066
So is it good sign
or a bad sign?

32:14.133 --> 32:15.434
Who knows?

32:15.501 --> 32:16.602
Good sign.

32:16.668 --> 32:17.703
The jury's out two days?

32:17.769 --> 32:18.804
That's a bad sign.

32:18.870 --> 32:20.139
Do you need
to take some time?

32:20.206 --> 32:22.541
Eh, better to stay busy.
But thanks, Lieutenant.

32:22.608 --> 32:24.676
All right, if you need
anything, let me know.

32:24.743 --> 32:26.979
Boy, she's all right, Grace.

32:27.046 --> 32:28.847
Nobody like her.

32:28.914 --> 32:30.416
Fucking hate to see her
make Captain.

32:30.482 --> 32:31.383
Are you serious?

32:31.450 --> 32:33.085
No telling who we'd
end up with.

32:33.152 --> 32:34.386
I feel the same way.

32:34.453 --> 32:38.224
Anything we can do to,
uh, fuck up her chances?

32:38.290 --> 32:39.958
Just keep doing
what we're doing.

32:40.026 --> 32:42.261
Jesus, you guys.
