32:42.328 --> 32:44.063
I'm just joking.
I mean, you know,

32:44.130 --> 32:45.397
we wish her the best.

32:45.464 --> 32:47.333
You know, she deserves
to make Captain, right?

32:47.399 --> 32:49.501
Fuck that.
It'd be a calamity.

32:49.568 --> 32:50.969
I'll light a candle.

32:52.104 --> 32:53.439
I've been informed

32:53.505 --> 32:55.474
