still deadlocked

32:55.541 --> 32:57.943
and that further deliberations
would be fruitless.

32:58.010 --> 33:01.213
Therefore, on the single
count of Murder Two,

33:01.280 --> 33:03.949
The People of California
versus Veronica Allen,

33:04.016 --> 33:05.717
I declare a mistrial.

33:05.784 --> 33:07.186
No jeopardy attaches.

33:07.253 --> 33:08.954
The defendant's bond
is released.

33:09.021 --> 33:10.656
What does that mean,
no jeopardy?

33:10.722 --> 33:12.158
