33:12.224 --> 33:13.459
That's not fair.

33:13.525 --> 33:15.027
Well, don't worry
about it yet.

33:15.094 --> 33:16.228
Let's celebrate
this victory.

33:16.295 --> 33:18.330
This is a good thing,
Ronnie.

33:20.099 --> 33:21.800
This is not over.

33:23.069 --> 33:24.170
Detective.

33:24.236 --> 33:26.004
Seven to five
for acquittal?

33:26.072 --> 33:27.873
Why would the next
jury find you

33:27.939 --> 33:29.641
