will weigh the odds

33:32.578 --> 33:35.047
- and cut his losses.
- The DA will re-try.

33:35.114 --> 33:36.415
I'll make it my mission.

33:36.482 --> 33:38.284
You are a dog with a bone.

33:38.350 --> 33:40.752
And you, Mrs. Allen,
are a liar and a murderer.

33:44.790 --> 33:47.793
