34:05.010 --> 34:07.646
- The tattoos. How'd you know?
- Documents in the van

34:07.713 --> 34:09.681
pertaining to a Staff Sergeant
William Meadows

34:09.748 --> 34:11.650
and letters addressed
to a Billy Meadows.

34:11.717 --> 34:13.085
He the deceased?

34:13.152 --> 34:14.986
Waiting on the autopsy
for an I.D.

34:15.053 --> 34:16.688
They're super
backed up over there.

34:16.755 --> 34:18.657
He the owner of this
little slice of heaven?

34:18.724 --> 34:20.759
We think so.
Any prints
besides Meadows?

34:20.826 --> 34:22.361
- A multitude.
- Coppers said

34:22.428 --> 34:24.396
the place was ransacked
after he died.

34:24.463 --> 34:25.797
Homeless
on homeless, right?

34:25.864 --> 34:27.299
Most likely.

34:34.506 --> 34:36.175
The people's
case was flimsy,

34:36.242 --> 34:37.476
and the jury agreed.

34:37.543 --> 34:39.111
Bet it was the men
voted to acquit.

34:39.178 --> 34:42.248
I hear you, brother.
I'd acquit that any day.

34:42.314 --> 34:43.582
They heard the testimony.

34:43.649 --> 34:45.851
They found Mrs. Allen
more compelling...

34:45.917 --> 34:47.286
